<div>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;">Explain legislations and regulations on Ongoing Monitoring requirements.&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;">Describe the appropriate account/payments/customer base screening procedures required to demonstrate compliance.&nbsp;</span></li>
